            <title>[THRIFT-206] ruby required field validation requires before read instead of after</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-206</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s a glaring bug in the original ruby required patch. The check of required field presence happens BEFORE deserializing, not after. This means unset required fields will always be null.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
